Customer Churn Prediction using Machine Learning (Python)
ğŸ” Project Objective
To build a machine learning model that can predict whether a customer will churn (leave the company) or stay, based on historical customer data from a telecom company.

ğŸ§  What is Customer Churn?
Customer churn refers to when a customer stops using a companyâ€™s services. Predicting churn helps businesses retain customers, reduce losses, and improve service.

ğŸ“Š Dataset Features (Example)
The dataset contains information like:
gender: Male/Female
SeniorCitizen: Whether the customer is a senior
Partner / Dependents: Relationship status
tenure: How long they've been a customer
PhoneService / InternetService / Contract
MonthlyCharges / TotalCharges
Churn (Target): Yes/No

