ğŸ› ï¸ Steps Performed
Data Loading: Loaded customer data using pandas.
Preprocessing:
Handled missing values
Encoded categorical variables
Scaled numeric features

Exploratory Data Analysis (EDA):
Checked churn distribution
Correlation analysis

Model Training:
Used models like Logistic Regression, Random Forest
Split data using train_test_split

Evaluation:
Used confusion matrix, accuracy, precision, recall

Model Saving:
Used pickle to save and reload the trained model

ğŸ§ª Sample Model Accuracy
Accuracy: ~85% (varies by dataset and preprocessing)

